casebody.data:
Monday, March 4, 1996

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

94-2254. Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Sullivan.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of respondent’s motion for continuance of hearing. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that respondent’s motion be, and is hereby, granted, and that a hearing before the court be held on March 19,1996.

Douglas, Resnick, and Cook, JJ., dissent.
